Various utilities to help with git:

gitflow-installer.sh
	A make-less installer for gitflow, intended for people without gcc, etc.

gitignore
	Template .gitignore

gitlog2csv-DDL.sql
	DDL for tables for holding a git log

gitlog2csv.pl
	Perl script to convert a git log to comma-delimited text

pre-commit
	Hook script to ensure Win/Mac compatible file names

post-checkout
	Hook script to fix file mod times on checkout or branch change

